# Daily Research Log Format

Use one Markdown file per day: `daily_YYYY-MM-DD.md`.

Articles and papers share the same item template; distinguish only with **자료유형**.

Full manual: `templates/daily_research_log_template.md` · Code rules: `src/daily_report.py`

## File header (once per file)

```
# 데일리 리서치 로그

날짜: YYYY-MM-DD
기록자:
총 항목 수: N건 (기사 n / 논문 n)
신뢰도 분포: A n건 / B n건 / C n건
```

## Daily Executive Summary

Add when there are **1+ items** in the day (auto pipeline always generates for 1+).

Structure (auto-generated):
- **분석 기준 키워드 (상위 3개)**
- **오늘의 공통 흐름** (one-line theme)
- Table: `| 관련도 | 항목 | 한 줄 요약 |` with **직접/간접** relevance
- Item links `[title](#slug)` must match `<a id="slug"></a>` before `### N. Title`
- **눈여겨볼 신호 (키워드 관점)** — up to 3 signals; explain **why** 직접/간접 (match trigger + keyword implication), **not** a repeat of the table one-liner
- **상충되는 정보**

Avoid vague filler in summary cells: no deictic subjects ("이 기술은"), no generic "importance emphasized", no "의문을 불러일으켰음"-style abstract reactions, no keyword definitions without article facts. One-liners must pack 5W1H facts (who/where/what/when/numbers) for market-research scanning.

## Item block (repeat per entry)

```markdown
<a id="anchor-slug"></a>
### 1. Title

- **자료유형:** 기사 / 논문 / 보고서(시장조사) / 공식발표(IR·정책) / 기타
- **출처:**
- **저자/발행기관:**
- **발행일:** YYYY-MM-DD
- **링크/DOI:**
- **요약 (영문 원문):** (optional for manual; auto includes en_summary_steps)
  - **Overview:** ...
- **요약 (한국어 번역):**
  - Fact bullets; noun-style endings. Past: -었음/-았음/-했음. Present: -함/-임/-됨. Never -습니다/-합니다/-ㅂ니다/-다
  - Last line: `(해석) ...`
- **신뢰도:** A / B / C (auto never assigns C)
- **태그:** #tag1 #tag2 (max 4)
- **비고:** analysis keywords · relevance (직접/간접) · matched keywords
```

## Tags (monthly report chapters)

#기술 #논문 #투자 #M&A #제품출시 #기업동향 #규제 #경쟁 #시장수치 #리스크 #전문가전망

## Credibility

- **A:** peer-reviewed journals, Tier-1 wire (Reuters/Bloomberg/AP), gov/international stats, Gartner/IDC/McKinsey
- **B:** preprints, industry media, secondary reporting, corporate IR/press releases
- **C:** anonymous sources, speculation, repackaged/unverified content — **manual entries only**

Full template: `templates/daily_research_log_template.md`
